headline: GTA Online
subtitle: 2X GTA$ & RP on DJ Missions
content:
Clubbers and ravers are always making requests of the DJ; its only right we hear the talent out every once in a while and indulge their whims. Keep an eye out for texts from English Dave or Tom Connors, as they’ll need help keeping Moodymann, Keinemusik and Palms Trax comfortable.

Whether it’s charged crystals, pizza, or prized personal belongings, bring them back swiftly and you’ll be rewarded with invaluable industry clout, plus an additional 2X GTA$ & RP.
